	e 4\\\, Issaquah\\\, WA 98027 (next to the Gaslamp Bar and Grill) \\nMaxim
	um Students: 16 \\nCost: $270 \\nInstructor: Ron Hippe \\nRon Hippe joined
	 Unexpected Productions in 1990 and has performed globally—from San Franci
